      "thinking": "The user wants me to continue a Thai blog post from where it left off. The last sentence was \"### หลักการที่ 2:\" and I need to continue with:\n\n1. หลักการที่ 2: Speaking-First Methodology\n2. หลักการที่ 3: Low-Affective-Filter Environment\n3. What This Means for Your Child section\n4. CTA section (Ready to Break the Cycle?)\n\nThe tone should be empathetic but scientifically authoritative, approximately 500-600 more words.\n\nLet me write this continuation in Thai, maintaining the blog's voice and structure.",
